    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infernal Chess 是一款黑暗幻想风格的国际象棋游戏，背景设定在地狱的火焰深处。在一个火山棋盘上与恶魔主题的棋子展开战斗，掌握战略玩法，在火热的地狱氛围中展开激烈对决！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/75db97962f5155e0bdeb7c4b34fd35f4.webp?t=1772360866\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/9966d67d0e4a8766f52670cbf82b0e9f.poster.avif?t=1772360866\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/9966d67d0e4a8766f52670cbf82b0e9f.webm?t=1772360866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/9966d67d0e4a8766f52670cbf82b0e9f.mp4?t=1772360866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Infernal Chess</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infernal Chess 是一款经典国际象棋的黑暗幻想版，背景设定在地狱深处的火山景观中。玩家将在一个独特的3D棋盘上进行战略性对战，每一步都被神秘氛围和富有生命力的恶魔主题棋子所增强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/42018114977d5d4139609a1536ddeb4b.webp?t=1772360866\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/e6ec957ca84215732ddf73c7e15a6a2a.poster.avif?t=1772360866\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/e6ec957ca84215732ddf73c7e15a6a2a.webm?t=1772360866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264310/extras/e6ec957ca84215732ddf73c7e15a6a2a.mp4?t=1772360866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供了一种视觉震撼的体验，将传统的国际象棋机制与丰富的黑暗幻想背景相结合。无论你是经验丰富的棋手，还是国际象棋新手，Infernal Chess 都会挑战你在这个策略与氛围交织的世界中超越对手。</p>",
